  "3193680": {
    "name": "Out of Hand: Deluxe",
    "steam_appid": 3193680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>Out of Hand</strong>》 是一款节奏快的派对动作游戏，玩家可以自由操控一只物理手感极强的手，搭配超带感的物理翻滚。2-8 名玩家在各种小岛上进行短暂激烈的对战，使用大量不同且有趣的道具制造混乱，争夺最后的胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>我们为什么制作 《Out of Hand: Deluxe》</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们是来自瑞典的两名好朋友，在大学期间玩了很多派对游戏。玩久了之后，大部分游戏都玩腻了，所以我们决定自己做一个。我们在 2023 年夏天毕业后，就把 《<strong>Out of Hand</strong>》发布在 Steam 上。当时游戏只支持本地多人，但大多数玩家都想和朋友在线玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >于是，我们花了整整 2024 年开发了在线多人模式。我们在开发过程中对游戏的方方面面都做了大量改进，因此，比起更新一个可能已经被遗忘的旧游戏，我们最终决定把它作为一款全新的游戏《<strong>Out of Hand: Deluxe</strong>》来发布。这样感觉会更加有趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在线与本地多人模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以和朋友在线游玩，或和沙发上的小伙伴一起用手柄在电视上畅玩，最多支持 8 名玩家同屏对战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/96f6990bbbcf592485527363224d88ba.poster.avif?t=1771949369\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/96f6990bbbcf592485527363224d88ba.webm?t=1771949369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/96f6990bbbcf592485527363224d88ba.mp4?t=1771949369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>基于物理的“神奇之手”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用你的手抓取地图上的各种道具，然后把它们扔向你的朋友！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/7bf54b5c3735e687cbc4e965afc74992.poster.avif?t=1771949369\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/7bf54b5c3735e687cbc4e965afc74992.webm?t=1771949369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/7bf54b5c3735e687cbc4e965afc74992.mp4?t=1771949369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>物理翻滚闪避</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随时使用翻滚动作化身为布偶，享受超搞笑的物理效果！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/c627023b7b3f18a336e64ae4d431e8cf.poster.avif?t=1771949369\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/c627023b7b3f18a336e64ae4d431e8cf.webm?t=1771949369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/c627023b7b3f18a336e64ae4d431e8cf.mp4?t=1771949369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>结合操作，制造混乱！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抓取道具 + 翻滚闪避 = 混乱加倍，快乐翻倍！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/a102f05c6edc3bd6f2c436de781d21c6.poster.avif?t=1771949369\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/a102f05c6edc3bd6f2c436de781d21c6.webm?t=1771949369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/a102f05c6edc3bd6f2c436de781d21c6.mp4?t=1771949369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可解锁的服装</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过完成成就解锁各种有趣的服装，打扮你的角色！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/c35bcceae9f19bd5c5da0d342a05e9dc.avif?t=1771949369\" width=616 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富多样的地图</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验超过 40 张独特地图，玩法多变，乐趣无限！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/6b7a2a8843efce55324798f5d2fc7a4e.poster.avif?t=1771949369\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/6b7a2a8843efce55324798f5d2fc7a4e.webm?t=1771949369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193680/extras/6b7a2a8843efce55324798f5d2fc7a4e.mp4?t=1771949369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
